    v0 = (0.40 + wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.68)))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.83 + v1 + 0.09) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.65)) * wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.34)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.23 - tmp + 0.85)))
